<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.5">
<l>kañcaṉaik kāyntāṉaik kaṇṇamaṅkaiyuḷ niṉṟāṉai,</l>
<l>vañcaṉappēy mulaiyū ṭuyirvāymaṭut tuṇṭāṉai</l>
<l>ceñcolnāṉ maṟaiyōr teṉṉaḻuntaiyil maṉṉiniṉṟa</l>
<l>vañcaṉakkuṉ ṟantaṉṉai yaṭiyēṉkaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself the one who killed Kamsa,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who stands in Kaṇṇamaṅkai,</l>
<l>The one who, sucking with his lips, consumed the life</l>
<l rend="indent">of the deceitful demoness through [her] breasts,</l>
<l>The kohl[-colored] mountain which stands eternally in Aḻuntai of the south</l>
<l>Where [live] experts of the well-worded four Vedas.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
